By":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"當年接近一挑全世界既優良血統<br />\n今日都要比條肥總理搞彎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc87b61133763142b00971a55f69555fecaf074","tid":581585,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"我返工個個月自動扣3x%人工 我諗唔係比廢老說係去左難民度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4127e747c9cfae6214c4c3a9696cc29d325b2f8a","tid":581585,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"計我話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該一入國就要每日指定勞動10小時，<br />\nEg做清潔工，工廠低端工<br />\n然後發飯券制<br />\n<br />\n唔做勞動（低端工作）既，女既姦，男既做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，然後送番去去對面國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> eg Israel"},{"pid":"6dcd6cda60f55bb77b08ed7849b158139ae78039","tid":581585,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"其實德國係 左膠國家 係好事<br />\n將來中共屠殺香港人,  香港人可以去德國做難民<br />\n<br />\n德國 連中東佬咁難頂都可以接受到<br />\n咁香港人一定無問題啦<br />\n<br />\n最起碼香港人唔會犯罪, 肯番工, 有禮貌"}]}